In the same way, we=E2=80=99ll have yearly Covid shots. Every year or two, =
the vaccine companies will use the amazing technology of mRNA to cook up va=
ccines specific to the latest variant, the FDA will approve them quickly, a=
nd lots of people will get these shots.=20
